---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
import { openSourceThanks, site, techNotes } from '../data/site';
---

<section id="tech" class="tech-section section-shell">
  <SectionHeading code="04" label="SMALL LAB" title="空闲时间，琢磨一点小玩意。" note="它们未必宏大，但每一次接线、点亮、测量和记录，都让下一次解决问题更快一点。" />

  <div class="lab-grid" data-reveal>
    {techNotes.map((note, index) => (
      <article class:list={['lab-note', { 'lab-note--wide': index === 0 || index === 3 }]}>
        <img src={note.image} alt={note.title} loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        <div>
          <span>{note.code}</span>
          <h3>{note.title}</h3>
          <p>{note.text}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>

  <div class="open-source" data-reveal>
    <div class="open-source__intro">
      <span>OPEN SOURCE / THANKS</span>
      <h3>谢谢那些愿意把经验公开的人。</h3>
      <p>很多学习和生活里的小问题，都是沿着别人留下的线索慢慢解决的。</p>
    </div>
    <ol>
      {openSourceThanks.map((item) => (
        <li>
          <a href={item.href} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <strong>{item.name}</strong>
            <span>{item.note}</span>
            <i aria-hidden="true">↗</i>
          </a>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="section-end" data-reveal>
    <p>持续学习，不假装什么都会。</p>
    <a class="arrow-link" href={site.github} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">去我的 GitHub 看看 <span>↗</span></a>
  </div>
</section>
